==English==
===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ʌ.lɑŋˈsaɪd/

===Adverb===
# [[Along]] or by the side; side by side with;&mdash;often with of; as, bring the boat alongside; alongside of him; alongside of the tree.
===Preposition===
# Together with or at the same time.
#: ''The nurse worked '''alongside''' the doctor.''
